            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> Licini</supplied>o <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> Cra<supplied reason="lost">sso Frugi</supplied> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">au</supplied>guri c<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>o</abbr><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">populus Da</supplied>mascen<supplied reason="lost">orum per</supplied> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">legatum</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>ni <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilium</ex></expan> et Sel<supplied reason="lost">eucenses Pieriae</supplied> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <supplied reason="lost">Μάρκῳ Λικινίῳ Μάρκου υἱ</supplied>ῶι Κράσσωι <supplied reason="lost">Φρούγει αὔγουρι ὑπάτωι</supplied> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">ὁ δῆμος ὁ Δαμασκηνῶν τῆς ἱερᾶς καὶ ἀ</supplied>σύλου καὶ <supplied reason="lost">αὐτονόμου καὶ συμμάχου</supplied> <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">Ῥωμαίων πρεσβεύσαντος <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>νου κα</supplied>ὶ ἡ πόλις <supplied reason="lost">ἡ ἱερὰ καὶ ἄσυλος καὶ αὐτόνομος</supplied> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">καὶ σύμμαχος Ῥωμαίων τῶν Σ</supplied>ελευκέ<supplied reason="lost">ων τῶν ἐν Πειερίαι</supplied>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwei aneinander passende Fragmente erhalten. (B): Marchetti Longhi, AE 1948: Abweichungen in Lesung und Ergänzung. Unterhalb des lateinischen Textes Wiederholung der Inschrift auf griechisch in kleineren Buchstaben.</p>
            </div>
